OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FJapan to sell fighter jets 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fin break from pacifism     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Japan's cabinet has approved the export
OL,6, of new fighter jets it is developing   
OL,7, with the UK and Italy, in the latest   
OL,8, move away from its pacifist policies.  
OL,10,FIt eased arms export rules to allow the
OL,11,Fjets to be sold to countries that Japan
OL,12,Fhas signed defence pacts with, and     
OL,13,Fwhere there is no ongoing conflict.    
OL,15,FJapan has pledged to double military   
OL,16,Fspending by 2027, citing threats posed 
OL,17,Fby China and North Korea.              
OL,19,FEach fighter jet sale will require     
OL,20,Fcabinet approval, authorities said.    
